Value (marketing)

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search






This article is written like a personal reflection or opinion essay that states a Wikipedia editor's personal feelings about a topic. Please help improve it by rewriting it in an encyclopedic style. (July 2010) (Learn how and when to remove this template message)




