Value Exchange International Inc.


            
            Value Exchange International, Inc. operates as a credit card processing and merchant-acquiring services company that provides POS-credit card clearing services to merchants and financial institutions in PRC and Hong Kong. It also provides of IP processing services in Asia to bank card-accepting merchants. The company markets its services to local merchants with regional retail locations across Asia Pacific as potential customers of their IP and related credit card and debit card processing systems. Value Exchange International was founded on June 26, 2007 and is headquartered in Hong Kong.

            
